<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px;">
  <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #333;">Welcome to Bravik Beta!</h2>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">Hi <strong><%= @user.first_name %></strong>,</p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
    You've been invited to try Bravik's AI-powered customer support platform! Your beta account has been created with full access to test our features.
  </p>

  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #007bff;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #333;">Your Login Details:</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <%= @temp_password %></p>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
    <a href="https://app.bravik.com.au/users/sign_in" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">Login to Bravik</a>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;"><strong>What you can do during your beta trial:</strong></p>
  <ul style="color: #555;">
    <li>Upload and manage documents for your AI assistant</li>
    <li>Customise your assistant's behavior and branding</li>
    <li>Generate embeddable chat widgets</li>
    <li>Monitor conversations and review flagged messages</li>
  </ul>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
    Please change your password after your first login for security.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
    If you have any questions or feedback during your trial, feel free to reach out to jamie@bravik.com.au
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">Welcome aboard!</p>
  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;"><strong>Bravik Team</strong></p>
</div>
